oracle.ateam.sample.mobile.util

Class ADFMobileLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.ateam.sample.mobile.util.ADFMobileLogger

  • public class ADFMobileLogger
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class to easily add log statements to your custom classes. To use this class, define a static field in your class as follows: 
     private static ADFMobileLogger sLog = ADFMobileLogger.createLogger(MyClass.class);
    Then you can add use this field to log messages at various levels.
